name: n0ter
description:
N0ter is an application that came from my personal disdain for the increasingly "web-only" society we live in. A long time ago, applications that didn't need to be on the internet, were NOT in the internet. They ran on our computers and that worked just fine like that. 
Nowadays, everything is online, all the data is in third party systems and we literally own nothing... 
This annoying reality, combined by my nostalgia for old style development (I've been working online for YEARS now only writing API's, Microservices, REST services, gRPC services, etc) made me decide to spend some of my free time slowly writing an application that ran completely offline and did one of the things I currently do on one of those "third party dependent systems", Note taking. 
Don't expect development to happen fast, and don't expect me to do things in a conventional way. This was mainly done by me, for me, not for you. The choice of technologies used is also unorthodox, so... Yeah... Enjoy... Or not!
